												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "She kisses the player softly, then hungrily.\r\n\r\nShe lowers herself to the sand, the player following. They embrace, the player on top of Shadowheart. She suddenly utters a small gasp of pain - \r\n\r\nSH squirms slightly to move off an offscreen pebble poking into her."
												}
											},
