				"speakerSlotDescription": [
					{}
				],
				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Shadowheart and the player go skinnydipping at a quiet cove near Baldur's Gate sometime after SH becomes an enemy of Shar. \r\nIn this scene, Shadowheart is feeling vulnerable after having been abandoned by her goddess, and seeks a moment of catharsis with the player - she had previously shared with them that she didn't know how to swim, and now wishes to reclaim a bit of herself after her identity as a shar follower is lost.\r\nShe and the player bond and a playful, tender romance scene ensues after the return to shore.\r\n\r\nMarking for rerecord for a more playful, teasing tone, less serious than the origial recordings."
				}
			}
		}
